INSERT INTO `questions` VALUES ('263', '117', 'Citrix 研发／技术支持内推（实习岗）', '这问题应该从哪里说起了，应该从徐大大（@徐子豪）要将友答变身中国版linkedin开始说起。。。。\n\n不少同学都私信问实习内推的事，先谈谈关于找实习求职的一些想法，后面欢迎补充拍砖。。。。\n\n1. 如果你觉得自己没有亮点，那就不断的思考，找到自己的亮点。\n2. 如果怎样思考都觉得自己没有亮点，那就想想怎样努力才能让自己有亮点。\n3. 亮点不止在技术方向，能跑下全马，会做饭，会跳舞也是亮点。要做自己的挖掘机。\n4. 不努力很可怕，但是没有方向光有努力也很可怕。\n5. 如果找到了亮点，请用一句话来概括你的亮点中的一个实例。\n6. 想想那亮闪闪的实例中，你做了些什么。除了你现在做的，还能做什么。\n\n\n如果大伙找我内推，可以将简历发给我，邮箱是liang333916@126.com. 祝大家都能找到心仪的实习。\n\n以下是需求描述，简而言之是看题说话。。。\n=======================================================================\nSoftware Engineer Intern\nJob Description:\n\n•	Help on Cloud/Virtualization products enterprise software development with the guide from supervisors, follow industry standard software development process.\n•	Implement and unit test with C++/C#/Java/PowerShell/Python for assigned module based on Windows/Linux operation system.\n•	Develop automation and supportability tools to increase efficiency and productivity. \n•	Identify, isolate and analyze issues. Troubleshoot and resolve problems found.\n•	Set up, configure and maintain the hardware and software test environment.\n•	Execute functional, system and automated test cases, record results and track the bugs until closure. \n•	Synchronize and communicate with teams on status, and actively report any found issue to team lead. \n\n\nRequirements:\n\n•	Bachelor’s degree or equivalent in computer science, electrical engineering, or related field.  Equivalent experience may be substituted for formal education.\n•	Understanding of Computer Science fundamentals (e.g. algorithms, data structures).\n•	Basic understanding of networking (TCP/IP) and data communications.\n•	Basic knowledge on Windows and/or Linux Operating Systems.\n•	Basic proficiency in a programming language(s) (e.g. C, C++, C#, Java, JavaScript, Perl, Python, PowerShell, .NET).\n•	Pass CET-6, or equivalent English skills, without any difficulty in reading/writing technical related English emails/articles. Fluent oral English is a plus.\n•	Must be a quick learner and team player.\n•	Can work as intern for 6 months or more\n•	Knowledge of Internet technologies (e.g. HTML, XML) and Database is a plus.\n•	Knowledge on iOS/Android is a plus.\n\nTechnical Support Intern\n\nPosition Summary\nThe technical support engineer positions will provide support service to customers who are working to implement Citrix products like XenServer, XenDesktop, XenApp and Netscaler.   The daily job is focusing on isolating problems, in-depth root cause analysis and providing solutions of Citrix products and their integration into customer environments. \nWe are looking for someone with very good Windows, Linux or networking skills and who is also eager to learn about virtualisation. \n\nRequirements (essential)\nAt lease strong in one of the following technical areas and professional communication\n•     Windows server and workstation operating systems skillset.\n•     Linux skillset\n•     Networking skillset\n•     Communication Skillset\n– Fluent in English.  Understand customer and good service sense.\nRequirements (nice to have)\n•     Programming\n•     Database\n•     Virtualisation  products and concepts\n•     Storage  (SAN/NAS, Raid)\n•     Any industry certificates of Microsoft, Cisco, Citrix or other companies.\n\n【如何在友答上发布实习招聘内推】 http://www.uanswer.me/?/question/510', null, '2015-04-12 21:58:52', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null);
