INSERT INTO `questions` VALUES ('562', '70', '【英特尔实习内推】Intel上海招聘Machine learning/Computer vision Intern', '我的组里最近还需要招两位实习生，主要从事机器视觉和人工智能方面的开发研究工作~~\n\nBelow is the JD for computer vision and AI interns:\nWe\'re hiring:\n    Machine learning/computer vision intern\n\n**Business Group Overview**\nBiTS (Binary Translation Software) department delivers binary translation software products for Intel. BiTS Shanghai owns the product development and delivery for applications on phones, tablets and servers, with world class quality. The team is innovating leading edge technology and exploring new exciting directions. \nBiTS department is part of the Software and Services Group (SSG), whose charter is delivering best user experience and best developer experience on all computing platforms throughout cell phone, tablet, PC and servers with Intel chips.\n\n**Job Description**\nWorking on a new product project, the candidate would be responsible for implementing a mechanical/electronic/software co-design product.  Challenging and interesting work which requires highly focus and devotion.  Highly motivated group with lots of fun.  Every member has the ability to directly affect product success and invent future technologies with out-of-box thinking.\n\n**Qualifications**\nWe are looking for candidates with qualifications in the following area:\n        Machine learning/Computer vision.  Candidate should present skill in machine learning, pattern recognition and computer vision.  \n        Experience on using OpenCV is a plus.\n        Experience on feature detection/matching, segmentation, deep learning, or reinforcement learning is a plus.\n        Experience on C++ programming is a plus.\n\nBesides area specific skills, we need candidates present skills in the following areas:\n1. Excellent development and troubleshooting skills\n2. Strong problem solving skills\n\nIf you are interested in this position, please send both your English and Chinese resumes to chong.yu@intel.com. Mail subject must start with &quot;BiTS Intern Application - Name&quot;.', null, '2015-04-12 21:58:52', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null);
INSERT INTO `questions` VALUES ('563', '70', '对于苹果新发布的macbook air大家怎么看？你喜欢去掉了风扇和只有一个USB-C接口的设计吗？', '12寸MacBook Air的设计\n\n苹果2015年发布全新12寸 MacBook Air ，这款设备相比以往的MacBook有着很大的不同。全新12寸 MacBook Air采用了新的设计，移除全尺寸 USB 接口、MagSafe 连接器和 SD 卡槽。不过，全新12寸 MacBook Air 会配备超高分辨率的显示屏。\n\n[attach]600[/attach]\n\n[attach]601[/attach]\n', null, '2015-04-12 21:58:52', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null);
